{"tid":1578930,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[an機] 有咩輸入法app可以寫簡體出繁簡雙選項?","createTime":"2019-09-18T10:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T14:29:52.000Z","uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"959244832f810722262d217768b4ebf338c0b856","tid":1578930,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:45:46.000Z","msg":"家母原先用iphone, 但最近壞機, 呢排手頭緊, 換咗an機用。<br />\n<br />\n但家母有一事不滿! 佢話: <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>點解輸入法唔係好似iphone咁,</strong></span></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">寫簡體, 同時有繁簡兩個選項, </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n之後小弟去搵，見好多輸入法app可以 寫簡出繁，但係就係唔能夠同時彈出繁簡字眼供選擇。<br />\n<br />\n想問吓有無咩app解決到呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好免費. 好用收費都可以考慮。"},{"pid":"82ca898c6e1fe719aec6ddd2786cc7d12d30a291","tid":1578930,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48da12a951256fce556d1b1f0842c03b5457e4e4","tid":1578930,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ca898c6e1fe719aec6ddd2786cc7d12d30a291","tid":1578930,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SDBtOO6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSDBtOO6.gif&h=a5a9e2f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似咁樣<br />\n<br />\n寫完[华]字，想要佢出华字又得，華字又得<br />\n寫完[国]字，想要佢出国字又得，國字又得"},{"pid":"dad084ac958e896e948c04dd9edd484e44ab75f9","tid":1578930,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48da12a951256fce556d1b1f0842c03b5457e4e4","tid":1578930,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":